+# AI Prompt: Build a Modern Counter dApp on Base Chain
+
+## Project Overview
+Create a sleek, modern decentralized counter application on Base blockchain with Farcaster Mini App integration. The app should feature real-time updates, gamification elements, and an exceptional user experience.
+
+## Core Requirements
+
+### 1. Blockchain Integration
+- **Network**: Base Mainnet (Chain ID: 8453)
+- **RPC**: Use public Base RPC or Alchemy
+- **Explorer**: Basescan (https://basescan.org)
+- **Native Currency**: ETH
+- **Smart Contract**: Deploy enhanced counter contract with NFT badges
+
+### 2. Design Philosophy
+**Modern, Premium Aesthetic:**
+- Dark theme with vibrant accent colors (purple/blue gradients)
+- Glassmorphism effects for cards and modals
+- Smooth micro-animations on all interactions
+- Responsive design (mobile-first approach)
+- Ambient background with subtle animated gradients
+- Neumorphic elements for depth
+
+**Typography:**
+- Primary font: Inter (clean, modern)
+- Monospace font: Roboto Mono (for addresses, numbers)
+- Large, bold counter display (6rem+ font size)
+- Clear hierarchy with varied font weights
+
+**Color Palette:**
+```
+Primary: #667eea → #764ba2 (gradient)
+Success: #10b981
+Error: #ef4444
+Warning: #f59e0b
+Background: #0a0a0a
+Surface: #1a1a1a
+Surface Elevated: #2a2a2a
+Text Primary: #ffffff
+Text Secondary: #a3a3a3
+```
+
+**Spacing & Layout:**
+- Generous whitespace
+- Max width: 600px for main content
+- Consistent 8px grid system
+- Rounded corners: 16px for cards, 9999px for buttons
+
+### 3. UI Components
+
+**Counter Display:**
+- Massive, animated number
+- Pulsing glow effect on changes
+- Smooth count-up/count-down animation
+- Real-time updates via WebSocket or events
+
+**Action Buttons:**
+- Large, tactile buttons with haptic-like feedback
+- Gradient backgrounds with hover states
+- Loading spinners during transactions
+- Disabled state with clear visual feedback
+- Icon + text labels
+
+**Wallet Connection:**
+- Single prominent "Connect Wallet" button
+- Support for: prefer reown appkit for wallet connection with project id ad03e2d8544cdf786495f370a5fc2e33
+  - Farcaster wallet (auto-connect in Mini App)
+  - Coinbase Wallet
+  - WalletConnect
+  - MetaMask
+  - Rainbow Wallet
+- Display connected address (truncated)
+- Show wallet balance
+
+**Transaction Feedback:**
+- Animated progress bar at top of screen
+- Toast notifications for all actions
+- Transaction hash with copy button
+- Link to Basescan explorer
+- Pending/Success/Error states with appropriate colors
+
+**Leaderboard:**
+- Top 20 users displayed
+- Animated entry/exit of positions
+- Highlight current user's rank
+- Show avatar (optional), address, action count
+- Smooth scrolling list
+
+**Badge System:**
+- Display current badge tier prominently
+- Badge icons with SVG animations
+- Progress indicator to next tier
+- Celebration animation on tier upgrade (confetti, particles)
+- Tooltip explaining tier requirements
+
+### 4. Features & Functionality
+
+**Core Actions:**
+- Increment counter (+1)
+- Decrement counter (-1)
+
+**Gamification:**
+- 7 badge tiers based on total actions
+- NFT badge minted on first action
+- Badge evolves with on-chain metadata
+- Leaderboard with real-time rankings
+- Achievement celebrations
+
+**Social Sharing:**
+- "Cast to Farcaster" button (native SDK integration)
+- "Share to Twitter/X" button
+- Pre-filled messages with counter value and badge tier
+- Include app link and relevant hashtags
+
+**Transaction History:**
+- Show user's last 5 transactions
+- Type (increment/decrement), timestamp, hash
+- Stored in localStorage per wallet
+- Clear, scannable list format
+
+**Admin Controls (Owner Only):**
+- Reset counter to any value
+- Update fee amount
+- Modify badge thresholds
+- Pause/unpause contract
+
+**Real-time Updates:**
+- Watch contract events
+- Auto-refresh counter every 10s as fallback
+- Update leaderboard on changes
+- Show live activity feed (optional)
+
+### 5. Technical Implementation
+
+**Tech Stack:**
+- Vite for build tooling
+- Vanilla JavaScript (ES6 modules) or React
+- Wagmi Core v2 for blockchain interactions
+- Viem for Ethereum utilities
+- Farcaster Mini App SDK
+- Reown AppKit (WalletConnect v2)
+- Tailwind CSS for styling
+
+**Smart Contract Interactions:**
+```javascript
+// Read operations
+- count(): Get current counter value
+- fee(): Get transaction fee
+- getUserStats(address): Get user's stats
+- getTopAddresses(): Get leaderboard addresses
+- getTopCounts(): Get leaderboard counts
+- userTokenId(address): Get user's badge NFT ID
+- tokenURI(tokenId): Get badge metadata
+
+// Write operations (payable)
+- increment(): Add 1 to counter
+- decrement(): Subtract 1 from counter
+
+// Owner operations
+- setFee(uint256): Update fee
+- resetCounter(uint256): Reset counter value
+- setBadgeThresholds(...): Update tier thresholds
+```
+
+**Event Handling:**
+- Listen to `CounterChanged` event
+- Listen to `BadgeAssigned` event
+- Listen to `CounterReset` event
+- Update UI immediately on events
+
+**Performance Optimizations:**
+- Lazy load components
+- Debounce auto-refresh
+- Cache contract reads
+- Minimize re-renders
+- Optimize bundle size with code splitting
+
+**Error Handling:**
+- User-friendly error messages
+- Retry logic for failed transactions
+- Network error recovery
+- Wallet connection fallbacks
+
+### 6. Animations & Interactions
+
+**Micro-interactions:**
+- Button press: Scale down to 0.98
+- Hover: Slight elevation, brightness increase
+- Focus: Colored ring (accessibility)
+- Loading: Spinner or skeleton screens
+
+**Counter Animations:**
+- Number change: Smooth interpolation over 500ms
+- Easing: Ease-in-out cubic
+- Glow pulse on update
+- Optional: Particle effects on milestone numbers
+
+**Badge Unlock Animation:**
+- Scale + rotate animation
+- Confetti/particle burst
+- Success modal with badge preview
+- Sound effect (optional, user preference)
+
+**Page Transitions:**
+- Fade in on load
+- Smooth scroll behavior
+- Staggered list item animations
+
+### 7. Accessibility
+
+- Semantic HTML5 elements
+- ARIA labels on interactive elements
+- Keyboard navigation support
+- High contrast mode support
+- Screen reader friendly
+- Focus indicators
+- Alt text for images
+
+### 8. Mobile Optimization
+
+- Touch-friendly button sizes (min 44x44px)
+- No hover-dependent interactions
+- Optimized for small screens
+- Fast loading on mobile networks
+- Works in Farcaster app webview
+- Responsive typography (clamp() for font sizes)
+
+### 9. Security Best Practices
+
+- Never expose private keys
+- Validate all contract addresses
+- Sanitize user inputs
+- Use secure RPC endpoints
+- Implement rate limiting on client side
+- Clear warnings for mainnet transactions
+- Transaction simulation before sending
+
+### 10. Testing & QA
+
+- Test on multiple browsers (Chrome, Safari, Firefox, Brave)
+- Test on mobile devices (iOS, Android)
+- Test in Farcaster Mini App environment
+- Test all wallet connectors
+- Test with low/high gas prices
+- Test error scenarios
+- Test with slow network
+
+### 11. Deployment
+
+- Host on Vercel
+- Custom domain setup
+- Environment variables for RPC, contract address
+- CI/CD pipeline
+- Analytics integration (optional)
+- Error tracking (Sentry, optional)
+
+### 12. Documentation
+
+Include README with:
+- Project description
+- Features list
+- Installation instructions
+- Usage guide
+- Contract addresses
+- Network details
+- Contributing guidelines
+- License
+
+### 13. Additional Features (Nice-to-have)
+
+**Enhanced UI:**
+- Dark/light theme toggle
+- Customizable accent colors
+- Sound effects toggle
+- Animation speed control
+
+**Advanced Features:**
+- Multi-language support (i18n)
+- Historical counter chart
+- User profile pages
+- NFT badge gallery view
+- Rarity score for badges
+- Community challenges
+- Referral system
+
+**Analytics:**
+- Total transactions
+- Unique users
+- Most active times
+- Counter velocity (changes per hour)
+- Badge distribution
+
+**Notifications:**
+- Browser push notifications for cooldown expiry
+- Farcaster notifications for badge upgrades
+- Email notifications (opt-in)
+
+### 14. Code Quality
+
+- Clean, commented code
+- Consistent naming conventions
+- Modular structure
+- Error handling everywhere
+- TypeScript (optional, for type safety)
+- ESLint + Prettier configuration
+- Git commit message standards
+
+## Deliverables
+
+1. Fully functional dApp
+2. Smart contract (deployed and verified on Base)
+3. Clean, documented codebase
+4. Deployment on Vercel
+5. README with setup instructions
+6. Demo video/screenshots
+7. Farcaster manifest configuration
+
+## Success Criteria
+
+- App loads in < 2 seconds
+- Smooth 60fps animations
+- Transaction success rate > 95%
+- Mobile responsive on all devices
+- Works flawlessly in Farcaster Mini App
+- Clean, modern aesthetic
+- Intuitive user experience
+- No critical bugs
+
+## Important Notes
+
+- Auto-detect environment and adapt
+- Use Base mainnet (real ETH transactions)
+- Ensure contract is upgradeable or thoroughly audited
+- Consider gas optimization in contract
+- Make UI elements large and touch-friendly
+- Add helpful tooltips throughout
+- Show loading states for all async operations
+```
+
+Generate an app logo and update the app metadata title and description.

